tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE WebsiteTraffic (
    VisitorID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    PageVisited VARCHAR(255),
    VisitDateTime TIMESTAMP,
    DeviceType VARCHAR(50),
    ReferrerPage VARCHAR(255),
    ConversionStatus BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE page_views (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  page_id UUID,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  device_type VARCHAR,
  browser VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE conversions (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  conversion_type VARCHAR,
  conversion_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  purchase_amount DECIMAL,
  product_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_metrics (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    visitor_ip TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_views INTEGER
)

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    action TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates (
    conversion_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    conversion_type TEXT,
    conversion_rate REAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
    session_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INTEGER,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
)
CREATE TABLE website_visitors (visitor_id INT, visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP, source_url VARCHAR(255), page_visited VARCHAR(255), conversion_goal BOOLEAN);
CREATE TABLE user_accounts (user_id INT, username VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(100), subscription_status BOOLEAN, last_login TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE traffic_sources (source_id INT, source_name VARCHAR(50), traffic_type VARCHAR(50), marketing_campaign VARCHAR(100), is_paid_source BOOLEAN);
CREATE TABLE conversion_metrics (conversion_id INT, visitor_id INT, conversion_timestamp TIMESTAMP, conversion_goal VARCHAR(50), conversion_value DECIMAL(10, 2));
CREATE TABLE page_views (view_id INT, visitor_id INT, page_visited VARCHAR(255), view_timestamp TIMESTAMP, time_spent_seconds INT);
